"``ndarray`` rich comparison operators"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/2.2.5-notes.rst:50
msgid ""
"`#28758 <https://github.com/numpy/numpy/pull/28758>`__: TYP: some "
"``[arg]partition`` fixes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/2.2.5-notes.rst:51
msgid ""
"`#28772 <https://github.com/numpy/numpy/pull/28772>`__: TYP: fix incorrect "
"``random.Generator.integers`` return type"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/2.2.5-notes.rst:52
msgid ""
"`#28774 <https://github.com/numpy/numpy/pull/28774>`__: TYP: fix "
